doctype html
html(lang='en')
  head
    title Frame - A user system API for Node.js
    meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0')
    link(rel='shortcut icon', href='favicon.ico')
    link(rel='stylesheet', href='public/build.css')
  body
    div.jumbotron
      h1.text-center Frame
      h2.text-center A user system API for Node.js
      p.text-center: a.btn.btn-primary.btn-lg(href='https://hapiframe.herokuapp.com/docs')
        |Live Demo on Heroku
      ul.project-links
        li: a(href='https://github.com/jedireza/frame/') View GitHub Project
        li Version 1.4.0
        li: a(href='https://github.com/jedireza/frame/zipball/master') Download Frame
      div.gh-btns
        iframe(src='http://ghbtns.com/github-btn.html?user=jedireza&repo=frame&type=watch&count=true&size=large', allowtransparency='true', frameborder='0', scrolling='0', width='135px', height='30px')
        iframe(src='http://ghbtns.com/github-btn.html?user=jedireza&repo=frame&type=fork&count=true&size=large', allowtransparency='true', frameborder='0', scrolling='0', width='125px', height='30px')
        iframe(src='http://ghbtns.com/github-btn.html?user=jedireza&repo=frame&type=follow&count=false&size=large', allowtransparency='true', frameborder='0', scrolling='0', width='173px', height='30px')
    div.container.marketing
      div.page-header
        h2.text-center Built-in Features
      div.row
        div.col-sm-4
          h3
            i.fa.fa-hand-o-right
            |  Signup
          p.
            The <code>/signup</code> endpoint makes sure the supplied username
            and email address are unique and creates new <code>User</code> and
            <code>Account</code> documents.
        div.col-sm-4
          h3
            i.fa.fa-sign-in
            |  Login
          p.
            When supplied valid credentials, the <code>/login</code> endpoint
            creates a new <code>Session</code>.  We've also included
            endpoints for resetting a forgotten password.
        div.col-sm-4
          h3
            i.fa.fa-paper-plane
            |  Email Utility
          p.
            The <code>/contact</code> endpoint demonstrates the built-in email
            utility. By composing Handlebars and Markdown, personalized emails
            with HTML and text parts share one template.
      div.row
        div.col-sm-4
          h3
            i.fa.fa-user
            |  Users &amp; Roles
          p.
            <code>User</code> documents store login credentials and roles.
            Frame ships with two roles; <code>Account</code> and
            <code>Admin</code>.
        div.col-sm-4
          h3
            i.fa.fa-users
            |  Admin Groups
          p.
            Frame also ships with an <code>Admin</code> grouping facility
            (<code>AdminGroup</code>). Think about these like departments;
            sales, support, manager, etc...
        div.col-sm-4
          h3
            i.fa.fa-key
            |  Permissions
          p.
            Permissions can be granted to an <code>AdminGroup</code> or
            individually for an <code>Admin</code>. <code>Admin</code>
            permissions will win over their group's permission.
    footer
